# Marginalia is a separate Yarn 4 project. The parent .gitignore covers
# the global stuff (node_modules, *.tsbuildinfo, marginalia/dist), but Yarn
# 4's local state lives inside this subdirectory and needs its own rules.

# Yarn 4 local state (per https://yarnpkg.com/getting-started/qa#which-files-should-be-gitignored):
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/sdks
!.yarn/versions

# Build output and TS incremental cache (parent .gitignore catches these too,
# but kept here for clarity if marginalia ever moves to its own repo).
dist/
*.tsbuildinfo
.vite/
